            <list>
               <item corresp="#lb6" xml:space="preserve">
            <ref>5</ref>
            <p>It is uncertain if the second letter is α or λ (see the latter's shape at l. 4). The scribe might have started writing χαχ or χλχ, then he realized the mistake and squeezed a λ between the second and the third character, keeping the preceding letter as α anyway. That he wrote χλ̣α̣χ for χαλχ is not to be ruled out completely.</p>
          </item>
